Well worth the price, the voice acting is a big plus for me and it has interesting story for such a game. I would recommend it if you like this artstyle and point-click games. I myself not a fan of this type of gameplay but enjoyed it a lot. 
MAJOR SPOILERS ahead;
[spoiler] The story took unexpected turn at the last two acts for me. I expected a solid/real explanation for most of the things and characters but some of them are still vague. Maybe a bit more explanation for supernatural elements could have created a better ending or maybe I jussed missed some things. Still not a bad ending. [/spoiler]

